f-the-west-bank/00000191-ce12-d214-a393-cfba5b7c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称，夜间从黎巴嫩向以色列发射了约 50 枚火箭弹；无人员伤亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article-live/reports-three-rescuers-killed-in-israeli-attack-in-lebanon-drone-sirens-in-north-israel/00000191-cf4f-d25e-a1f7-cfcff8cb0000</link><description>以色列各地数十万人在抗议一周后呼吁达成释放人质协议 ■ 中央情报局局长：致力于以色列与哈马斯停火协议，这是一个政治意愿问题 ■ 以色列国防军瞄准加沙学校设立的哈马斯指挥中心的恐怖分子；巴勒斯坦报告：4 人死亡、25 人受伤 ■ 巴勒斯坦司机在约旦河西岸撞上警车后被捕；无人员伤亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 01:54:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article-live/reports-three-rescuers-killed-in-israeli-attack-in-lebanon-drone-sirens-in-north-israel/00000191-cf4f-d25e-a1f7-cfcff8cb0000</guid></item><item><title>法院命令释放涉嫌向本格维尔扔沙子的女子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/woman-suspected-of-throwing-sand-at-ben-gvir-released-by-court-order/00000191-ce49-d25e-a1f7-cfcb46e60000</link><description>特拉维夫地方法院法官在观看该事件的短视频后中断听证会，随后将嫌疑人软禁，因为整个法庭都在抗议对她的拘留</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 21:50:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/woman-suspected-of-throwing-sand-at-ben-gvir-released-by-court-order/00000191-ce49-d25e-a1f7-cfcb46e60000</guid></item><item><title>随着数字影子战争的加剧，以色列军队高层成为错误信息的焦点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-09-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-digital-shadow-war-intensifies-israeli-army-brass-is-in-misinformation-crosshairs/00000191-ccaf-d214-a393-cdbfa9210000</link><description>亲巴勒斯坦的账户发起了一场心理战运动，为巴勒斯坦人提供了短暂的胜利形象，声称以色列国防军高级军官死亡。研究人员将这些错误信息活动追溯到俄罗斯</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 17:44:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-09-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-digital-shadow-war-intensifies-israeli-army-brass-is-in-misinformation-crosshairs/00000191-ccaf-d214-a393-cdbfa9210000</guid></item>