vir-held-in-jail-overnight/00000191-cbc4-d359-a5f9-dfed93970000</link><description>地方法院接受了警方的说法，即如果嫌疑人被释放，调查可能会受到影响。嫌疑人的母亲在X上写道：“独裁警察决定危及我患有慢性疾病的女儿的生命”</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 09:47:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/woman-suspected-of-throwing-sand-at-ben-gvir-held-in-jail-overnight/00000191-cbc4-d359-a5f9-dfed93970000</guid></item><item><title>以色列狱警拍摄虐待被拘留者的视频；监狱部门称这是一次“例行演习”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-guards-filmed-abusing-detainees-prison-service-says-its-a-routine-exercise/00000191-cb71-d359-a5f9-dffd26f60000</link><description>《国土报》获得的照片和视频显示，数十名被拘留者戴着手铐趴在地上，其中一些人赤身裸体，一只看门狗在他们上方狂吠。监狱内并没有发生什么异常事件促使狱警采取行动</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 08:24:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-guards-filmed-abusing-detainees-prison-service-says-its-a-routine-exercise/00000191-cb71-d359-a5f9-dffd26f60000</guid></item><item><title>报道：三名救援人员在以色列对黎巴嫩的袭击中丧生；以色列北部的无人机警报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article-live/palestinians-idf-gunfire-kills-13-year-old-girl-in-west-bank-following-settler-clashes/00000191-c8fb-d74e-aff9-ccffedac0000</link><description>以色列各地数十万人在抗议一周后呼吁达成释放人质协议 ■ 中央情报局局长：致力于以色列与哈马斯停火协议，这是一个政治意愿问题 ■ 以色列国防军瞄准加沙学校设立的哈马斯指挥中心的恐怖分子；巴勒斯坦报告：4 人死亡、25 人受伤 ■ 巴勒斯坦司机在约旦河西岸撞上警车后被捕；无人员伤亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 20:56:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article-live/palestinians-idf-gunfire-kills-13-year-old-girl-in-west-bank-following-settler-clashes/00000191-c8fb-d74e-aff9-ccffedac0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人：定居者冲突后，以色列军队在约旦河西岸开枪打死 13 岁女孩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/palestinians-idf-gunfire-kills-13-year-old-girl-in-west-bank-following-settler-clashes/00000191-c8ea-d12d-a191-fbfa0ec60000</link><description>这名 13 岁女孩的父亲说，她是在家里的房间里被袭击的。目击者称，枪击事件发生前，定居者与以色列国防军爆发了冲突，定居者投掷石块并放火焚烧田地。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 20:02:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/palestinians-idf-gunfire-kills-13-year-old-girl-in-west-bank-following-settler-clashes/00000191-c8ea-d12d-a191-fbfa0ec60000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨和艾森科特对抗内塔尼亚胡，但很难击败骗子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-09-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/gantz-and-eisenkot-take-on-netanyahu-but-its-hard-to-beat-a-crook/00000191-c81b-d12d-a191-fb1b12860000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 18:13:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-09-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/gantz-and-eisenkot-take-on-netanyahu-but-its-hard-to-beat-a-crook/00000191-c81b-d12d-a191-fb1b12860000</guid></item><item><title>由于对以色列国家监管机构缺乏信心，爆炸性的加沙战争报告被束之高阁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/lack-of-faith-in-israels-watchdog-leaves-explosive-gaza-war-reports-in-the-drawer/00000191-c773-d4f1-adb7-dff787f80000</link><description>军方认为，战时的批评可能会削弱其表现，司法部长也同意这一点。更重要的是，国家审计长马塔尼亚胡·恩格尔曼被视为本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的傀儡，他热衷于将自己的缺点归咎于他人</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 18:13:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/lack-of-faith-in-israels-watchdog-leaves-explosive-gaza-war-reports-in-the-drawer/00000191-c773-d4f1-adb7-dff787f80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 336 天：联合国称加沙人道主义局势“超出灾难性”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-336-un-says-humanitarian-situation-in-gaza-beyond-catastrophic/00000191-c7e8-d12d-a191-fff8a74b0000</link><description>布林肯表示，加沙休战条款已达成近 90%，调解员将在未来几天内向以色列和哈马斯提出新建议 ■ 哈马斯发布被谋杀的以色列裔美国人质赫什·戈德堡-波林的视频 ■ 据报道，以色列军队枪杀了美国人- 约旦河西岸抗议活动中的土耳其人权活动人士 ■ 这是战争开始 336 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 16:06:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-336-un-says-humanitarian-situation-in-gaza-beyond-catastrophic/00000191-c7e8-d12d-a191-fff8a74b0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人：美国土耳其活动家在约旦河西岸被以色列军队枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-reports-american-turkish-activist-shot-dead-by-israeli-soldiers-in-west-bank/00000191-c7f1-df27-a9b9-fffb3dab0000</link><description>该活动人士参加了贝塔的示威活动，自 2021 年定居者埃维亚塔尔前哨基地在贝塔建立以来，该活动每周都会举行。以色列国防军表示，它向一名向士兵投掷石块的人开枪，并正在调查这一事件</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 15:55:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-reports-american-turkish-activist-shot-dead-by-israeli-soldiers-in-west-bank/00000191-c7f1-df27-a9b9-fffb3dab0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长告诉最高法院，允许内塔尼亚胡亲自挑选公务员局长是非法的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/allowing-netanyahu-to-handpick-civil-service-chief-is-illegal-ag-tells-top-court/00000191-c79d-dd1b-a7db-f7df3f0d0000</link><description>总检察长要求法院暂停内阁的决定，称这可能会使专员依赖总理而不是公众</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 15:28:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/allowing-netanyahu-to-handpick-civil-service-chief-is-illegal-ag-tells-top-court/00000191-c79d-dd1b-a7db-f7df3f0d0000</guid></item><item><title>两名贝都因以色列人说，以色列国防军士兵在他们在约旦河西岸开车时殴打了他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/two-bedouin-israelis-say-idf-soldiers-beat-them-while-they-were-driving-in-west-bank/00000191-c704-df27-a9b9-ff9ea1b00000</link><description>这两个人说，士兵在前往耶路撒冷的途中拦住了他们，命令他们下车，用步枪抵住他们的头，并用枪殴打他们。当他们因受伤要求去医院时，一名士兵威胁说如果他们转身就开枪打死他们</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 12:30:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/two-bedouin-israelis-say-idf-soldiers-beat-them-while-they-were-driving-in-west-bank/00000191-c704-df27-a9b9-ff9ea1b00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院暂停本-格维尔晋升因对抗议者施暴而接受调查的警官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/court-halts-ben-gvirs-promotion-of-police-officer-accused-of-violence-against-protesters/00000191-c703-de0a-afd5-df4be6440000</link><description>法官裁定，梅厄·苏伊萨的晋升“明显偏离了警方的法律和专业审查程序”。 Suissa 目前正在接受犯罪调查，其中包括向 2023 年反司法改革抗议者投掷眩晕手榴弹</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 11:40:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/court-halts-ben-gvirs-promotion-of-police-officer-accused-of-violence-against-protesters/00000191-c703-de0a-afd5-df4be6440000</guid></item></channel></rss>